{"tid":598353,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔知唔知咩叫free thinking","createTime":"2018-03-19T12:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T04:27:30.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"da2803dda17d636e132d43acf14b448257b9eee4","tid":598353,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"在連登學術台，一係膠文，一係叫春文，一係科普文。<br />\n<br />\n正經少少學術討論，就叫人又citation又evidence，當晒係大學論文咁<br />\n<br />\n大老，識唔識乜叫free thinking和free thinker ?<br />\n<br />\n識唔識尊重下free thinking culture<br />\n<br />\n知唔知道 benefit of free thinking <br />\n<br />\n香港社會咁落去真係唔店，病態<br />\n<br />\n個社會又係<br />\n做過office assistant, clerical assistant成批大學生做<br />\n<br />\n教育將普通人培訓成人才，再將人才浪費"},{"pid":"bdda11435ab92385dfdaed0b1373d852ca4f58e1","tid":598353,"uid":47480,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"我淨係知你青山走出黎"},{"pid":"498a5dd480da6803cd863476f9a3703961a3efca","tid":598353,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"香港人真係，一係就真膠，一係就認真<br />\n<br />\n不懂半認真，半膠半認真<br />\n<br />\n唉......"},{"pid":"901c21ba36ad305ab8d9f0a6e9a3cb7e60769ae9","tid":598353,"uid":164167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦"},{"pid":"975f2123b37bebbf6e5db5103570fa9a9f135fff","tid":598353,"uid":1103,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"如果你講既free thinking可以完全唔需要evidence，其實同9up有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫你講每一句話都要cite sources，但如果你講既嘢對方唔相信/懷疑，而你又唔願意比證據同埋來源，好難唔懷疑你係唔係9up。"},{"pid":"965953cb014cf73f0388b0ebe73868f0249a30ba","tid":598353,"uid":1103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"975f2123b37bebbf6e5db5103570fa9a9f135fff","tid":598353,"uid":1103,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"如果你講既free thinking可以完全唔需要evidence，其實同9up有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫你講每一句話都要cite sources，但如果你講既嘢對方唔相信/懷疑，而你又唔願意比證據同埋來源，好難唔懷疑你係唔係9up。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:07:46.000Z","msg":"我並冇貶低9up既價值，但唔好用其他字眼包裝到9up係好嚴謹既deliberation"},{"pid":"08fb1c5a6b4cb75f631cf3ed835546afa68759cf","tid":598353,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/210748_b6ff1cbbaa5d8533d52cfd6773cce147.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F210748_b6ff1cbbaa5d8533d52cfd6773cce147.png&h=d7b70eee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/210750_fcf94f0902e0743c57b4dcd1e27b519a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F210750_fcf94f0902e0743c57b4dcd1e27b519a.png&h=361b153f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/210751_452304cabcb844b5d185e96e7f6fc6b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F210751_452304cabcb844b5d185e96e7f6fc6b6.png&h=2aa0689a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/210753_bea1a8d2205fbd12588e8149463e4178.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F210753_bea1a8d2205fbd12588e8149463e4178.png&h=872dd8d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47e5965cf2254413bf36c89c969cd5e7e47e292e","tid":598353,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"975f2123b37bebbf6e5db5103570fa9a9f135fff","tid":598353,"uid":1103,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"如果你講既free thinking可以完全唔需要evidence，其實同9up有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫你講每一句話都要cite sources，但如果你講既嘢對方唔相信/懷疑，而你又唔願意比證據同埋來源，好難唔懷疑你係唔係9up。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"冇話唔需要evidence<br />\n<br />\nfreethinking係來自歐洲<br />\n當時係宗教和教會主導緊思想<br />\n當你講科學，懷疑上帝，無疑就係提出異議，你就係free thinker<br />\n<br />\n但講返連登學術台<br />\n基本上只要係對主流意見提出異議<br />\n即係free thinking<br />\n都被屌到爆<br />\n無論係另類自療又好，中醫又好，史觀又好，政見都好<br />\n所以連登仔係唔肯接受 free thinking <br />\n<br />\n你講大陸好勁，係香港環境都係 free thinking<br />\n因為香港人自我感良好，覺得自己比大陸強<br />\n但連登仔唔接受 會封你做五毛<br />\n<br />\nfree thinking的相反係group thinking"},{"pid":"de5447db3c1c5d3247d7d50318f01acb09c7028c","tid":598353,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T01:30:36.000Z","msg":"Freethinker的下場<br />\n<br />\n在中世紀歐洲，做freethinker，批判當時的主流思想（宗教、教會、公教）：被火燒<br />\n<br />\n在中國文革，批判當時主流思想（馬克思思想、毛澤東思想、中共黨的思想）：勞動改造，思想改造，坐監<br />\n<br />\n在現代中國，批判政府主流思想（共產黨好、一黨專政好）：被和諧（禁言），嚴重者或要坐監（參見劉曉波）<br />\n<br />\n在連登，批判連登核心主流思想（反共、反中、親西方、反另類治療）：一眾巴絲怒屌，五毛狗"},{"pid":"258832bdf7a507608024be4053335866e10cdd21","tid":598353,"uid":33938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"你有你講 我有我笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關你撚事"},{"pid":"ca9f5a5cd3e4544e3de3992a694f41b60bc21dc8","tid":598353,"uid":1103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47e5965cf2254413bf36c89c969cd5e7e47e292e","tid":598353,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"975f2123b37bebbf6e5db5103570fa9a9f135fff","tid":598353,"uid":1103,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"如果你講既free thinking可以完全唔需要evidence，其實同9up有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫你講每一句話都要cite sources，但如果你講既嘢對方唔相信/懷疑，而你又唔願意比證據同埋來源，好難唔懷疑你係唔係9up。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"冇話唔需要evidence<br />\n<br />\nfreethinking係來自歐洲<br />\n當時係宗教和教會主導緊思想<br />\n當你講科學，懷疑上帝，無疑就係提出異議，你就係free thinker<br />\n<br />\n但講返連登學術台<br />\n基本上只要係對主流意見提出異議<br />\n即係free thinking<br />\n都被屌到爆<br />\n無論係另類自療又好，中醫又好，史觀又好，政見都好<br />\n所以連登仔係唔肯接受 free thinking <br />\n<br />\n你講大陸好勁，係香港環境都係 free thinking<br />\n因為香港人自我感良好，覺得自己比大陸強<br />\n但連登仔唔接受 會封你做五毛<br />\n<br />\nfree thinking的相反係group thinking"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T04:27:30.000Z","msg":"如果你意思係「願意reasoning到the best explanation既thinker」，我冇咩理由要反對。"}]}